{"tid":2243940,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA21 Ultimate Team 不推文討論區 (20) 不推文中walkout","createTime":"2020-10-15T06:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T09:57:38.000Z","uid":128648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f43bf0ab1067d8e828cbd9f7f8225a82a599bb9d","tid":2243940,"uid":128648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T06:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FckjBrs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFckjBrs.gif&h=bb509340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家加入FIFA21 Ultimate Team討論區<br />\n<br />\n開始前請先睇Q&amp;A，睇完搵唔到你想知嘅野先問，好多你想知嘅野都係第一版！拜託曬！<br />\n<br />\nFIFA UT web app: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/37RdeGm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37RdeGm&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=3b85c928\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37RdeGm</a><br />\n<br />\n球員資料database:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://futbin.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffutbin.com&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=e6c86c79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://futbin.com</a><br />\n<br />\nSBC 答案 (參考idea, 抄足貴到仆街)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/36xts7Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36xts7Q&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=fba0e9fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36xts7Q</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n1.幾時有預購嘅包送？<br />\n答:每逢星期一朝早<br />\n<br />\n2. 點賺錢?<br />\n答:踏實d, 打比賽, 要快手就去課coins, 但EA話會嚴打買賣coins, 後果自負<br />\n玩耐左可以試下炒卡。<br />\n留意賣卡會收「稅」，成功交易會抽5%，如賣10,000 coins成交，實收9,500<br />\n<br />\n3. 咩係chemistry?<br />\n答:簡單d黎講, 高chemistry d隊員走位好d唔會成碌木咁唔走位, 另外個人chemistry會影響能力<br />\n<br />\n4. 咁點加chemistry呀?<br />\n答:位置、球員之間嘅連線、教練、loyalty等等都會影響chemistry。<br />\n<br />\n5. 咩係綠色連線?<br />\n答:球員同球員之間ge連線:國籍,聯賽,球隊<br />\n符合兩樣就夠有綠色連線<br />\n<br />\n6. 咩係IF?咩係TOTW?點解有d卡會係黑色?<br />\n答:每星期三晚都會有新嘅TOTW (team of the week)<br />\n出嘅人會有張加強版嘅黑色卡，又叫IF (in form)<br />\n<br />\n7.chemistry style係咩黎?持續幾耐?<br />\n答: 唔同chemistry style會對球員某d 能力有唔同提升, 每個球員一開始都有basic呢個style<br />\n你會見到每項能力都有一格V形箭嘴, chemistry style卡係永遠套用於某個球員, 直至你apply另一張落去<br />\n<br />\n8: 你地成日講H/H, H/M, M/L 係乜勁呀?<br />\n答: 代表球員work rate, H-high, M-medium, L-low<br />\n<br />\n9: 乜野係ONE TO WATCH呢？<br />\n答: 就係呢個球員今季先轉會，咁就有幸比FIFA觀察<br />\notw卡 係會跟inform卡 upgrade數值，卡面都會跟埋IF<br />\n<br />\n10:我DR SB 幾分幾分夠唔夠KEEP RANK 1?<br />\n答:<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2oMWQ9m\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2oMWQ9m&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=fe7b7c22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2oMWQ9m</a><br />\n<br />\n11:點樣開新po？<br />\n答: 去#1右上角三點，禁以此內容開新主題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMetqpP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMetqpP.png&h=603a033d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12:頭5場WL 有咩用? 究竟WL 係點配對手俾我? <br />\n頭5場對手係random但決定你的起手ranking<br />\n贏曬即係+5 赢3場即係+1+1+1-1-1 &gt; +1 已經有極大既分別<br />\n<br />\n13:咩叫肥料卡，META卡？<br />\n答:肥料就係作用解SBC、靚國藉靚聯賽、高rate低能嘅人。META=實用球員，唔受總分所限 , 玩家覺得勁嘅卡<br />\n<br />\n14:藍卡，RTTF又係啲乜？<br />\n答: 藍卡 = UCL 卡 , 有得打歐冠先有嘅卡/RTTF = ROAD TO THE FINAL, 踢緊歐聯嘅球員 , 佢每晉一級就會升一分總分<br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/3735GB0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3735GB0&h=ed0af756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n15:點解我交唔到SBC/做唔到OBJ？<br />\n答: 開機交/睇英文版<br />\n<br />\n16:點link Twitch?<br />\n答: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/37M8hhT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37M8hhT&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=3c289bc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37M8hhT</a><br />\n<br />\n17:咩叫OBS? 點樣set?<br />\n答: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2v3TX7k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2v3TX7k&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=14d26dfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2v3TX7k</a><br />\n<br />\n18: SB太難打可以點?<br />\n答: 今年SB 如果難度揀Legendary or above，佢會根據pro player打法黎同你玩。熄 - 遊戲主頁面, Setting -&gt; Game Setting -&gt; Competitor Mode: OFF<br />\n<br />\n19: 點樣睇自己個club嘅球員consumables chemistry呢啲嘢?<br />\n答: 轉會&gt;轉會清單&gt;L3<br />\n<br />\n20: 咩叫執紙皮?<br />\n答: arbitrage 即係risk free profit, 係呢個market 入面其實有個bid-buy now spread 係到 所以如果你留心d 睇下邊d card 係有好多人要用黎做sbc 但係就無咩人bid 你就可以賺個差價, 但呢個spread 好多時會拉近/無得好快 所以最後可能只會每張賺1,200coins<br />\n<br />\n21: 今季有咩meta好用?<br />\n答: <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAOvTXP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAOvTXP.png&h=476b2070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y0yYfjF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY0yYfjF.png&h=e6518997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LBppBac.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLBppBac.gif&h=dfaa4189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我愛EA！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kJ7nFg0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkJ7nFg0.jpg&h=5df15dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEzeubT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEzeubT.jpg&h=5ab8e313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qeAknx5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqeAknx5.jpg&h=a0496d52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1HRCP3m.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1HRCP3m.gif&h=9797a6dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zRSCREj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzRSCREj.jpg&h=68b00460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</p>"},{"pid":"386ba7506a0c1b59697b709dc5bd67d527603500","tid":2243940,"u